column2: select top # objid, ra, dec, petroR5#_r, petromag_r, BrightestObjin1#R5# from (select  objid, ra, dec, petroR5#_r, petromag_r,  (select max(p.petromag_r)  from dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(photoprimary.ra,photoprimary.dec,#*photoprimary.petroR5#_r) n join photoprimary p on p.objid = n.objid) as BrightestObjin1#R5# from photoprimary)
